text: Armuchee ( ) is an unincorporated community in both Floyd County and Chattooga County, Georgia, United States. The community is located along U.S. Route 27, north of Rome. Armuchee has a post office with ZIP code 30105. ==History== A post office called Armuchee has been in operation since 1837. The community takes its name from nearby Armuchee Creek. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Floyd County, Georgia Category:Unincorporated communities in Georgia (U.S. state)
